queries: select periodTypeName as tab, section, fiscalyear as x, value as y from api_schema.Companies_Financials where section != 'assets' and periodTypeName = 'Annual' order by x desc limit 6;

select periodTypeName as tab, section, fiscalyear, fiscalquarter as x, value as y from api_schema.Companies_Financials where section != 'assets' and periodTypeName = 'Quarterly' order by periodenddate desc limit 8;
